data.description: 4 Bedroom, 2.5 Bathroom Home with over 2,700 sqft of living space with an oversized garage, and fenced-in backyard on an approx—5,000 sqft lot. High ceilings and an open floor plan that amplifies the sense of spaciousness. Waterproof luxury flooring seamlessly combines beauty with practicality. The kitchen has 42' soft-close cabinets, granite countertops, and premium stainless steel appliances, including a stove complete with a handy pot-filler. The primary suite is LARGE, a retreat designed for serenity, offering his & hers walk-in closets, and check out the bathroom!... A double vanity, a jetted tub, and a separate shower that invites relaxation at the end of a busy day. Located just minutes from Downtown Norfolk and major interstates
